    "name": "Redneck Brawl Turbo",
    "steam_appid": 1858680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/ac4fd687a41351db3856b34e187432c5.poster.avif?t=1763017207\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/ac4fd687a41351db3856b34e187432c5.webm?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/ac4fd687a41351db3856b34e187432c5.mp4?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《红脖乱斗Turbo》</strong> 是一款轻松的自动射击游戏，背景设定在一个古怪的世界，灵感来自于80年代的武术喜剧电影。你将扮演一位必须拯救村庄的汉子，对抗一波又一波古怪敌人，赚取金币，并向功夫大师、醉拳师傅和白忍者学习强力技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/78e943a19b7dbce5c5f636d62033fb8a.poster.avif?t=1763017207\" width=620 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/78e943a19b7dbce5c5f636d62033fb8a.webm?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/78e943a19b7dbce5c5f636d62033fb8a.mp4?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为传奇</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是村里最强的男人——Pal，追捕偷走“繁荣之像”的忍者。探索狂野丛林、阴暗贫民窟、炽热沙漠等各种场景，迎战流氓、罪犯、机器人甚至外星人等疯狂敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拜见师傅们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/f56a7b3167ca339bb3f71320dc1cdd15.avif?t=1763017207\" width=620 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>功夫大师</strong>：掌握气的艺术，学习如何将气能转化为毁灭性武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>醉拳师傅</strong>：风格怪异但实用，这位师傅会教你使用破坏性道具进行创意战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>白忍者</strong>：用解魔方锻炼出的智慧大脑，他将传授你各种生活秘籍，例如用汽车电池复活自己等神奇技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/2694c28151b672682d77df0c4364236d.poster.avif?t=1763017207\" width=620 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/2694c28151b672682d77df0c4364236d.webm?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/2694c28151b672682d77df0c4364236d.mp4?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>幽默搞笑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作不仅有爽快的玩法，更充满了幽默元素。从爆笑剧情到荒诞描述，笑点无处不在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>变强之路</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/3077f80b01036fb0df39304347d9a7a7.poster.avif?t=1763017207\" width=620 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/3077f80b01036fb0df39304347d9a7a7.webm?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/3077f80b01036fb0df39304347d9a7a7.mp4?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >举铁、跑圈、练身体，成为无法阻挡的力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>好兄弟们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/e749842fbc881351633ef951408ceeff.poster.avif?t=1763017207\" width=620 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/e749842fbc881351633ef951408ceeff.webm?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/e749842fbc881351633ef951408ceeff.mp4?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来到村庄的酒馆，那里是兄弟们聚集的地方。请他们喝上一杯泡沫丰富的饮品，他们就愿意替你去执行任务。每位兄弟都有自己独特的个性或技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>休闲娱乐</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/a968a48034b954ecf814858d227ee1de.poster.avif?t=1763017207\" width=620 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/a968a48034b954ecf814858d227ee1de.webm?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858680/extras/a968a48034b954ecf814858d227ee1de.mp4?t=1763017207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村庄酒馆里有很多事情可以做：<br>● <strong>钓鱼池</strong>：捕捉并收集43种不同的鱼类。<br>● <strong>宝箱</strong>：用你的开锁技巧开启宝藏箱。<br>● <strong>幸运转盘</strong>：试试手气，赢取丰厚奖品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>手绘美术</strong>：每一关、每个角色和技能都是手工绘制，打造独特的视觉体验。<br>● <strong>流畅动画</strong>：数百个精细骨骼动画，让动作在慢动作下依然丝滑自然。<br>● <strong>技能自定义</strong>：混搭功夫大师的技巧：组合45种技能，或匹配成15种超级技能。打造适应特定场景的强力Build！<br>● <strong>破坏性道具</strong>：使用醉拳师傅提供的12种独特装置，每种都有不同的战术优势。<br>● <strong>多样敌人</strong>：迎战98种敌人，包括雪人、忍者、老奶奶、黑帮、疯子、机器人、外星人等。<br>● <strong>强力Boss战</strong>：挑战35个独特Boss，从骷髅、朋克、到龙、博士、超级战士、外星母舰、终结者T-300。<br>● <strong>丰富关卡</strong>：探索13个独特场景，如原始丛林、罪恶贫民区、北极苔原、机器人工厂、异域沙漠等。<br>● <strong>任务挑战</strong>：完成195个任务，获得气能与奖杯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你准备好和 Pal 一起踏上这段史诗冒险了吗？<br>村庄的命运，就掌握在你手中！</strong></p>",
